&lt;h3&gt;Shabbat Parashat D&#039;varim, Shabbat Chazon&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Shacharit Torah Reading&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deuteronomy 1:1-3:22 (P 1317, RP 1161, WTC 1041)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7 Aliyot&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Shacharit Haftarah&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Isaiah 1:1-1:27 (P 1180)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Haftarah&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Notes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the third of the three Haftarot of rebuke that we read between the Shiva Asar b&#039;Tammuz and Tisha b&#039;Av. This Haftarah should be read as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1:1  Haftarah cantillation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1:2-15  Eicha cantillation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1:16-19  Haftarah cantillation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1:20-23  Eicha cantillation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1:24-27  Haftarah cantillation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Mincha Torah Reading&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deuteronomy 3:23-4:8 (P 1333, RP 1188, WTC 1065)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3 Aliyot&lt;/p&gt;
